==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''preference'''
# the [[selection]] of one thing or person over others
# the [[chance]] to so [[select]], and the one [[selected]]
# the state of being [[preferred]] over others
# a strong [[liking]]
# [[preferential]] [[bias]]; [[partiality]]


